With the recent budget cuts announced by Governor Parsons, its CRUCIAL to our school district that Prop K.I.D.S. passes! Please encourage and remind your friends & family to get out and VOTE YES for Prop K.I.D.S. tomorrow, June 2.

Prop K.I.D.S. will NOT increase the tax rate!

Polls are located at Joachim Plattin Ambulance and will be open from 6 am - 7 pm.
